                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7136" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1110</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8513 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">力矩优行：一波三折的海外营销之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Twists and Turns of Lijuyouxing’s Overseas Marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨红，杨蕊竹，常秀云</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苏州力矩优行智能科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小企业；国际市场营销；营销观念；国际市场细分战略；“塔型”营销组合策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Small and medium-sized enterprises; International marketing; International market segmentation strategy; Tower marketing mix strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大量中小企业在政策鼓励下走向海外市场寻找机会，谋求发展。资源有限和国际市场经验匮乏使其在推广自主品牌的路上步履维艰，在与外商交易中难以掌握自主权。本案例回顾了以经营“电助力自行车”为主的力矩公司自成立之初至今的曲折营销之路。以其“海外营销初探”、“出师不利未果而返”、“再度扬帆终有起色”作为主线，描述了公司创立、产品研发、在海外推广自主品牌的艰辛历程，以及最终只能先通过OEM形式与北美的品牌商进行合作,以站稳市场的决策和实施过程。本案例旨在引导学员树立科学的国际营销观念，思考如何结合中小企业的实际特点和外部环境条件来合理确定目标市场、科学制定国际市场营销策略；同时也为其他意在开拓海外市场的中小企业提供有益的借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">A large number of small and medium-sized enterprises are encouraged by policies to seek opportunities and development in overseas markets. Limited resources and lack of experience in the international market make it difficult for the company to promote its own brand, and it is difficult to master the autonomy in dealing with foreign investors. This case reviews the tortuous marketing road of Liju Company, which is mainly engaged in &quot;electric power bicycle&quot; since its establishment. With its &quot;overseas marketing study&quot;, &quot;got off failed and return&quot;, &quot;set sail again eventually improve&quot; as the main line, describes the company, product research and development, the hardships in the overseas promotion of independent brands, and ultimately only through the OEM form first cooperate with north American brands, to gain the market decision-making and implementation process. This case aims to guide students to establish a scientific concept of international marketing, thinking about how to combine the actual characteristics of small and medium-sized enterprises and external environmental conditions to determine the target market, scientific development of international marketing strategy; At the same time, it also provides useful reference for other small and medium-sized enterprises to develop overseas markets.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《国际市场营销学》、《市场营销》、《国际商务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销观念；国际营销环境分析；国际市场细分战略；利基市场；中小企业国际营销；“塔型”策略；撇脂定价法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
